This is a pong game in Python, made by SmartViking.

Packages required to play (*nix users):
python 2.7.18 or python 3.9
python2-pygame or python-pygame

WINDOWS USERS:
If you don't already have Python installed, get the Windows binary here (either 32 or 64 bit is fine) - http://www.python.org/getit/
After you have installed Python, get the appropriate pygame Windows binary here (install 32 or 64 bit, depending on which version of python you installed: http://www.lfd.uci.edu/~gohlke/pythonlibs/#pygame
MAC USERS:
You should already have Python installed, just download a version of python-pygame - http://pygame.org/download.shtml

Testing done:
- Tested with python 2.7.8 and 3.9.0
- Tested with pygame 1.9.6 and 2.0.0
- Tested with Arch Linux, Debian 6, Fedora 15 and Ubuntu, should work for all.
- Tested on Windows 7 x64, with Python 2.7 x64 with pygame 1.9.2 pre. 
- Tested on latest OS X with python 2.6 and pygame 1.9.2 pre

TODO:
